data.description: Introducing an exquisite residence in the prestigious Somerset, The Plantation community. This remarkable POOL HOME offers a rear east-facing orientation with beautiful sunrises providing perfect natural light, 2 BR, a large den, a Florida room, and 2 BA. Gourmet Kitchen, 42"cabinets with soft close drawers, pull-outs, quartz countertops, wall ovens, glass surface stove top, and large island. Enjoy quiet time in your Florida room looking out to the lake or soaking up the Florida sunshine while taking refreshing dips in the pool. This home has tray ceiling, crown molding, and large tile throughout. Spacious master bedroom with large walk-in closet, master bath has dual sinks, walk-in shower, and quartz counter. The home is storm season ready with Kevlar hurricane screens & accordion window shutters on all exterior windows. Beautiful custom ceiling lights/fans, and Hunter Douglas shades.The Plantation is an active community, private Hurdzan-Fry Championship 18-hole golf course,Clubhouse & restaurants. Newly remodeled Amenity Center with resort-style pool/spa, tennis/pickleball, bocce, & fitness center. Great Location near shopping, dining, & airport. COME ENJOY THE FLORIDA LIFESTYLE!
